translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_2c3ba748:
    # "As the tiresome work dragged one, Sarah lifted her head from her desk."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_c51cde82:
    # "Time had passed and turned and by now she worked by candlelight."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_a087e249:
    # "When the words and letters on the pages began to shift and twist, she knew she had reached her limit."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_393c80c4:
    # "Sarah fell back in her chair and turned her eyes towards the ceiling."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_f9d88709:
    # "Even the ceiling seemed to dance."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_14aa2669:
    # "Sarah closed her eyes."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_838deb35:
    # "Slowly, a peace came over her."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_7e404277:
    # "So far from home. So isolated. Alone."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_2e40a930:
    # "There were her soldiers. Her servants. Her attendants."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_f8d4a085:
    # "She was not truly alone, but all the people that meant most to her in the world were so very distant."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_f5f6f6b1:
    # "Somehow, being surrounded by people only seemed to make her feel more lonely."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_63a026f8:
    # "But with her eyes closed, she could dream easy."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_a49e9aeb:
    # "And things like time and place meant so very little."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_fa2e0518:
    # "Her husband. Her children."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_b496707d:
    # "When she held her eyes closed, Sarah could swear they were so close she could reach out to them."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_e1aa765d:
    # "She opened her eyes and looked at the desk again."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_539a862b:
    # "Suddenly, she reached over and grabbed one of the blank pages."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_672cbbe4:
    # "Placing it in front of her, pressed the tip of her pen to the paper and began to write."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_61c53779:
    # s "Dear husband."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_b2ee1933:
    # s "I write you from my study in Queen Maeiv's castle."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_db1ec701:
    # s "All my needs have thus far been well seen to. The room. The celebrations. The beautiful gardens."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_c288d9f1:
    # s "Yet rather than enjoying any of them, I find myself only saddened."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_d799b7af:
    # s "Once I walked this world by myself, and all that I saw and loved were my own to cherish."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_5970bee0:
    # s "But now, I find myself haunted by you, even as we are countless distances removed."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_2871cd7d:
    # s "As I walk the gardens, I find myself instinctually looking over my shoulder."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_2ac92bcd:
    # s "To see you. Look for you. Share a glance and moment."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_fa581c63:
    # s "It is odd to me, even after all these years, that I can speak more with you in a gesture than I can speak with most in a conversation."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_31ba6a64:
    # s "Before you, I never had what we now have."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_074bca3d:
    # s "I never missed, what now so pains me."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_56b0816e:
    # s "You were an absence for most of my early days, but it is only now that I can feel the absence in my heart."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_ce376b90:
    # s "If my position were different, I would call upon the guards and make way for home this instant."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_0a990867:
    # s "To see you. To see our children. To be home, in every sense."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_c74ac605:
    # s "But duty has yoked each of us apart from one another."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_2d393013:
    # s "And so, again, I sit here writing to you from this cold and lifeless study."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_89df90d4:
    # s "Longing to fall asleep so that I may sooner begin to dream. In my dreams, I am home."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_4812065f:
    # s "My dreams, where I can see and smell and touch every part of you, as though we were never seperated."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_bb8f686c:
    # s "Even just the thought of your hands on my body solicit from me a reaction."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_0d062e3f:
    # s "My own attempts to imitate your touch with my own hands, leave me yearning only for the real thing."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_4964ba23:
    # s "Each night when I touch myself, my only fantasies are memories of our encounters."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_6da0ae7a:
    # s "I sketch you from memory, your arms, your chest, your shoulders."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_3429ab04:
    # s "Every part of you."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_d63a3fea:
    # s "And yet no joy or pleasure can rival the truth of you."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_d4401c70:
    # s "Varga."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_a5ff50d2:
    # s "Each peak tasts only of after-climax, as I try to take comfort in the hollow imitation."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_a0acc68e:
    # s "Instead, I find myself only more desperate to be re-united with you."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_eb83ff74:
    # s "To again press my hands on yours. Your lips on mine."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_35c2296f:
    # s "Every day and night. No matter time or distance. I am forever yours."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_a01166b8:
    # s "Dreaming of you..."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_ec62e28e:
    # s "Yours, forever, Sarah."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_12f6d353:
    # "Sarah quickly folded the letter, placed it in an envelop and sealed it with her royal seal."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom9intermezzo1_4883d983:
    # "It would travel across the continent, into the hands of the only man who had any right to see it."
    ""

